body.description: Sandcastles, farms, and roadways are ready to be imagined and built in your child’s sandbox with these John Deere construction vehicle toys. Watch your kids take their outdoor toys to new heights with this pair of officially licensed farm toys. This 2-pack includes a John Deere dump truck featuring a working dump bed and John Deere tractor with a working front loader. Made of heavy-duty plastic and featuring child-friendly designs, these durable John Deere toys are the perfect size for small hands and great for both indoor and outdoor play. Perfect for the sandbox because of their durable plastic construction and child friendly designs, this vehicle two pack is ideal for children ages 18 months and older. Outfitted in the popular John Deere green and yellow color scheme, these vehicles feature free rolling wheels and fully functional parts (moving dump bed and front loader). Watch as their imagination grows as they create different ways to play with this dump truck and toy tractor combo.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 15, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This is a really nice set of play sand vehicles and the perfect size for our 2 1/2 year old grandson and our green turtle sand box. Not too big for the sand box and not too small for his little hands. Well made. Easily cleaned. Holds just the right amount of sand for a shovel full or two. Nice bright colors. Good purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars My great grandson (18 months old) loved these
reviews.reviewText: Solid construction and fun for him to play with. Should last a long time.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very durable - and a perfect size
reviews.reviewText: Bought these for a 20 mo old grandson. He loves them. I gave him a tray with some dried beans and he scoops and dumps for hours. These are well made and just the right size for his small hands.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 28, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These are well made, a great size, and my one year old loves them! The pieces feel solid, not flimsy or like they’re going to fall apart. The moving parts operate cleanly. They’re the perfect size to haul a couple of my son’s Little People animals. I would definitely recommend these to anyone considering buying them.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Dumb Dump, corrected.
reviews.reviewText: The dump on the truck opens too easily. If you hold the dump from the top the bottom truck swings open. If sand is loaded too far in the back of the dump the sand falls out. So, I corrected this by adding a piece of adhesive cork between the dump and the frame. Easy fix. Now the dump can adjust to any position automatically. It is more fun and interactive. The manufacturer could easily change the plastic design to end this problem in the future. It is a nice looking fun toy, especially when combined with the front loader tractor.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 27, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I am actually so shocked on the quality of these tractors for the price! Everything on them is functional and such a perfect little set for a 1 year old that loves tractors. So so happy with them.
